Package MCO2

Class SpecialVM

java.lang.Object
MCO2.RegularVM
MCO2.SpecialVM
public class SpecialVM extends RegularVM
The SpecialVM class represents the Regular Vending Machine which contains all of the features of a Regular Machine. Which means that the SpecialVM is inherited from the RegularVM class. This includes the slot, items that can be stored in a slot and the changebox.
